Have you been collecting the beans?
You can grab one monthly on its own or along with other exclusive pin club pins.
We still have some left of every type so if you sign up now, you'll be able to catch up on previous beans! 
But once they're gone we won't be restocking!
Every bean comes with a matching transparent sticker!
.
www.stamistudios.com/pinclub
.
.
.

node.text:
🍥 NEW PRODUCT 🍥
Super excited to reveal the second new fur bag coming next Friday (13th)!
Pre-orders will be for a limited time and there will be a discount if you order both bags as well as a free pre order gift for the first 200 orders!
They are just PERFECT for trips out when you don't want to lug too much around with you - and looks super cute too!
The faux fur is so soft and we have even added a cute egg zipper detail.
Sign up to our newsletter and/or turn notifications on to not miss out 💕
.
.
.
